766
01:03:39,440 --> 01:03:45,080
the stronger you get. And I feel like another 
benefit of your approach is if you work at just  

767
01:03:45,080 --> 01:03:50,520
B2B SaaS companies, if you have too many of that 
on your resume, it's very hard to get hired a  

768
01:03:50,520 --> 01:03:57,840
consumer company. And so just having it creates a 
huge optionality for you if you do, which you did.

769
01:03:57,840 --> 01:04:02,840
Yeah, it's interesting because people used to 
talk about people who are T-shaped or whatever,  

770
01:04:02,840 --> 01:04:09,120
