804
01:06:49,640 --> 01:06:55,720
And so that was why I said earlier that at the 
end of the day, product management is at times  

805
01:06:55,720 --> 01:07:04,080
the worst job in the world and at times easily 
the best. And it's both and it can be both. And  

806
01:07:04,080 --> 01:07:09,280
so it's hard for me to think about if I think 
about the things that are the intersection of  

807
01:07:09,280 --> 01:07:13,360
what I'm good at and are valuable to the world, 
product management is a pretty fun one to do  

808
01:07:13,360 --> 01:07:17,480
and it's different every day. So I think we're 
pretty privileged. For those of you who listen,  

809
01:07:17,480 --> 01:07:21,320
I mean, obviously your podcast reaches a lot of 
