01:12:48,360 --> 01:12:54,840
them I guess because they're very valuable to me. 
One is that if you let your calendar rule you,  

873
01:12:54,840 --> 01:12:59,200
then nothing good will happen. I know people talk 
about that a lot, but it's surprisingly common in  

874
01:12:59,200 --> 01:13:03,040
